Original: 不知何時開始有100元商業午餐了，cp值超高，可以一試
EN: I don’t know when I started to have 100 yuan commercial lunch. The CP value is super high. You can try it.

Original: 餐點道地，味道十足，店員介紹詳細，期待未來能有更多樣化的餐點^_^
EN: The meal is full, the taste is full, the clerk introduces it in detail, and I look forward to more diverse meals in the future^_^
